body.description: Trusted by parents, Flintstones Multivitamin for kids have been providing kids nutritional support as they grow up healthy and strong for more than 50 years. Flintstones Vitamins with extra Iron for kids contains 15 essential vitamins and minerals in easy-to-chew, fruit-flavored tablets. These daily kids chewable multivitamins provide vitamins and minerals that growing bodies may need and have as much iron as about 15 cups of cooked kale. Flintstones Chewable Vitamins for kids have key nutrients to support physical energy by helping convert food to fuel, while also supporting bone health, immune health, and eye health. These fun kids chewable multivitamins feature eight classic Flintstones characters. Plus, the Flintstones brand has been trusted by parents for over 50 years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for vegetarians
reviews.reviewText: We're raising our kids vegetarian, and that often comes with a struggle to maintain proper iron levels. We therefore appreciate this "extra iron" version of the classic Flintstones vitamins. They have all the major vitamins and minerals that our kids would get from vegetables if they liked vegetables, and also the iron that they need. The flavor is good enough that our kids don't mind eating them at all.
